metadata.name: Limbo
metadata.description:
«give me a song

spend sad hours with me

get me wrong

crumpled hugs…»

Limbo is a place for lost souls, who are not allowed into either heaven or hell. A place for souls, who love each other regardless of gender, age or social status. And one day you want to be there.

…

This unique NFT includes a huge original painting (162x162 cm, acrylic on canvas) and worldwide shipping.
